Replies.Content:
PSG definitely hit GODTIER this week. Hopefully it can keep its momentum going into the next several weeks. Having an actual plot (which, knowing Gainax, will somehow become crazily warped, unless they’ve already used up their Holy Shit Quota) will no doubt help on that.

Squid Girl turned the moe up to 11, but OreImo 6 gives it a run for its money and turns it up to about 10.5. It’s a shame Manami x Kyo can never happen due to the show’s premise.

;\_;
